## Console memory models (memsy-core)

Returned by `client.memories.*`.

### `MemoryScopeInfo`

```python
@dataclass
class MemoryScopeInfo:
    level: str               # "org" | "role" | "team" | "actor"
    actor_id: str | None = None
    team_id: str | None = None
    role_id: str | None = None
```

### `MemoryItemResource`

