**Description:** Create an account, provision an organization, and generate your first API key.

Before you can use the SDK you need a Memsy account, an organization, and an API key. Everything below happens in the dashboard at **[app.memsy.io](https://app.memsy.io)**.

  
  

  

  

  

## Rotate or revoke a key

Back in **Settings → API Keys** you can rotate any key at any time. A revoked key stops working immediately; rotation issues a new key and leaves the old one working until you delete it.

